com.xrtb.pojo

Class Bid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xrtb.pojo.Bid

  • public class Bid
extends java.lang.Object
    POJO for a bid object. Use the HTTP payload of the bid and convert it into this object. This is used for debugging and in the JUNIT tests. This class is used to conveniently build a bid object from a string. This is a GSON based de-serializer.
